feature_list.title: Hot-swap
feature_list.article: The Year of the Rat keyboard is based on the newest version of Ducky's hot-swap keyboard. Hot swapping is the replacement or addition of components to a computer system without stopping, shutting down, or rebooting the system.

feature_list.title: 3 level angle adjustment keyboard stand
feature_list.article: Two-step keyboard feet allow you to set your keyboard at three different tilt angles.
